
## CONVERTIBLE TOP REMOVAL/INSTALLATION  


1. Cover both sides of the rear window glass with thick cloth to protect the window. 
2. Disconnect the negative battery cable. 
3. Remove the scuff plate. 
4. Remove the quarter trim. 
5. Remove the rear package trim. 
6. Remove in the order indicated in the table. 
7. Disconnect the rear window defroster power-cut switch. 
8. Install in the reverse order of removal.  

